```dockerfile
FROM maven:3.9-eclipse-temurin-21-alpine AS builder
WORKDIR /app
COPY pom.xml .
RUN mvn dependency:go-offline -DskipTests
COPY . .
RUN mvn clean package -DskipTests

FROM eclipse-temurin:21-jre-alpine
WORKDIR /app

# Install runtime dependencies: fonts for PDF report generation and curl for health checks
RUN apk add --no-cache fontconfig ttf-dejavu curl && \
    rm -rf /var/cache/apk/*

# Copy the built JAR from builder stage
COPY --from=builder /app/target/*.jar /app/app.jar

# Import AWS RDS root CA certificate
RUN wget -O /tmp/rds-ca.pem https://truststore.pki.rds.amazonaws.com/rds-ca-bundle.pem && \
    keytool -import -noprompt -alias rds-ca -file /tmp/rds-ca.pem \
    -keystore $JAVA_HOME/lib/security/cacerts -storepass changeit && \
    rm /tmp/rds-ca.pem

# Import Azure DigiCert certificate
RUN wget -O /tmp/digicert.crt https://cacerts.digicert.com/DigiCertGlobalRootCA.crt && \
    keytool -import -noprompt -alias azure-digicert -file /tmp/digicert.crt \
    -keystore $JAVA_HOME/lib/security/cacerts -storepass changeit && \
    rm /tmp/digicert.crt

# Create non-root user
RUN addgroup -S appgroup && adduser -S -u 1001 -G appgroup app

# Set ownership of application directory
RUN chown -R app:appgroup /app

USER app

EXPOSE 3000

LABEL maintainer="analytics-team@example.com"
LABEL org.opencontainers.image.description="Java Analytics Dashboard (Metabase)"

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=10s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:3000/api/health || exit 1

CMD ["java", "-jar", "/app/app.jar"]
